1973;;Showdown;;American;;George Seaton;;Dean Martin, Rock Hudson, Susan Clark;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Showdown_(1973_film);;Childhood friends Billy Massey and Chuck Jarvis go in opposite directions after Chuck ends up married to Billy's former sweetheart. Billy becomes a bank robber, Chuck a lawman. But they end up joining forces against common enemies in a final showdown.